<!-- wp:heading {"fontSize":"large"} -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading has-large-font-size">Opencart vs. WooCommerce: Comparative Statistical Examples</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Popularity: According to Google search trend statistics over the last 12 months, WooCommerce has been more searched for compared to Opencart.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":481,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none","align":"center"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-large"><img src="https://devmanextensions.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/trends-12-meses-opencart-vs-woocommerce-1024x414.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-481"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Trends of last 12 months. In red WooCommerce and in Blue OpenCart</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":2} -->
<ol start="2" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Loading Speed: A comparative study of loading speed was conducted between both platforms using the PageSpeed Insights tool. Both sites were hosted on the same hosting provider (Webempresa). The results demonstrated that WooCommerce has a slower average loading time compared to Opencart.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":484,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none","align":"center"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img src="https://devmanextensions.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/velocidad-carga-opencart.png" alt="" class="wp-image-484"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Insights of Opencart</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":485,"sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"none","align":"center"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image aligncenter size-full"><img src="https://devmanextensions.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/velocidad-carga-woocommerce.png" alt="" class="wp-image-485"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Insights of WooCommerce</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":3} -->
<ol start="3" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Number of Plugins/Extensions: WooCommerce's plugin library offers more than 10,000 options, whereas Opencart has approximately 6,000 available plugins. This indicates that WooCommerce, despite having a larger community, relies heavily on extensions and plugins, negatively affecting performance for medium and large-scale stores.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

